WEBVTT

00:08:29.199 --> 00:08:30.920
they could have broken the pact.

00:08:30.944 --> 00:08:32.094
But they didn't.

00:08:32.464 --> 00:08:34.032
And on April 3 this year,

00:08:34.056 --> 00:08:36.237
at exactly 8pm German time,

00:08:36.261 --> 00:08:39.738
we published simultaneously
in 76 countries.

00:08:40.220 --> 00:08:47.203
(Applause)

00:08:51.640 --> 00:08:55.252
The Panama Papers quickly became
one of the biggest stories of the year.

00:08:55.276 --> 00:08:58.480
This is the scene in Iceland
the day after we published.

00:08:58.504 --> 00:09:00.648
It was the first of many protests.